snippet.title: Tamara’s Timeless Beauty
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel!  My channel aim is to focus on Healthy Aging, Grateful Aging, Pro Aging..looking and feeling our best at any age.  I have a deep passion for all things involving skincare, make up, health and wellness. Having recently turned 61, I have a lifetime of knowledge and experience to share.  I am super excited  to be creating and posting videos on skincare, natural youthful makeup, favs and fails, reviews, and tutorials.  I post once a week on Sunday morning.  Join me and let’s have fun!

Contact info:  
tamarastimelessbeauty@yahoo.com
